Made Workflows view use a fixed two-column layout (HStack + divider) so the workflow list/detail pane is no longer user-resizable and no longer shifts sizes when selecting workflows. Added WorkflowsLayoutStabilityTests to cover this layout behavior.

Tests: ran swift test before/after; both fail in this environment with baseline issue `no such module 'XCTest'` (first seen in AddTaskProjectPreselectionTests.swift).